doc_summary_long: Don't worry, Mom. Yahoo is not changing its name to Altaba. Contrary to some news reports on Monday, only the part of Yahoo that is not being sold to Verizon will be renamed 'Altaba'. In addition, Yahoo CEO Marissa Mayer is to step down from its board, but will continue to be CEO.
doc_summary_short: Don't worry, Mom. Yahoo is not changing its name to Altaba.
doc_title: It's OK, guys. Yahoo is not changing its name to Altaba
